g.text: Focusrite plc., which comprises the Focusrite, Focusrite Pro, ADAM Audio, Novation and Ampify Music brands, announced the acquisition of Martin Audio Ltd and associated companies
RCF Group, one of the fastest growing groups in the professional audio market, has announced that it has completed the acquisition of Montarbo, an historic brand in the sector.
Biamp announced the acquisition of ‘Apart Audio’ & ‘Community Loudspeakers’ as a move to position itself as a full-line provider of AV solutions.

QSC announces the acquisition of Attero Tech which combines the Q-SYS audio, video and control (AV&C) Ecosystem with Attero Tech’s networked AV endpoints and I/O peripherals, as well as boosting QSC’s development capabilities
